 minutes before serving."}],"hintsAndTricks":["Please refer to the Mushroom stock paste recipe on this recipe chip or <i>The Basic Cookbook<\/i> for the Vegetable stock paste recipe.","With a cheesy, umami flavour, nutritional yeast contains all nine essential amino acids, is a great source of B vitamins and is often fortified with vitamin B12 (important for those following a vegan diet). You can find nutritional yeast at health food stores or online."],"basicInfo":["easy","20m","1h 30m","6 portions"]}